.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.env
secrets/
**secrets/
*secret*
*password*
*credential*
*.key
**/*.key
*.pem
**/*.pem
*.p12
*.pfx
*.crt
*.cer
*wallet*
*mnemonic*
*seed*
private*
privkey*

# =============================================================================
# VALIDATOR KEYS (CRITICAL - NEVER COMMIT)
# =============================================================================
validator*
**/validator*
!**/validator*/README*
!**/validator*/.gitkeep
publisher.key
testnet-keys/
generated-keys/

# =============================================================================
# SMART CONTRACTS - DO NOT INCLUDE COMPiled artifacts
# =============================================================================
# Note: Source contracts are in the repo, but build artifacts are ignored
out/
**/out/
cache/
**/cache/
foundry.lock
**/foundry.lock
deployments/local/
deployments/anvil/
broadcast/
**/broadcast/

